(28, '10/100M Fiber Media Converter ST Singlemode Single Fiber 1310/1550nm 25KM', '', 4, 0, 1, '', 1, '2017-10-09 02:14:56', 1507478400, NULL, '<p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;"><strong>MAIN DESCRIPTION</strong></span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">10/100Mbps adaptive fast Ethernet Optical Media Converter, with built-in 2 ports 10M/100Mbps</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">self-adaptive switch, converting the 2 independent 10Base-T or 100Base-TX twisted pair electrical</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">signal with 100Base-FX optical signal. It extends the network transmission range from 100m, the</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">l</span><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">imit of copper line, to 120Km (single mode full duplex). It supports two different types of network</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">connection media, 10/100Base-TX and 100Base-FX. By switching technique and storage &amp; forwarding</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-