(32, '10/100/1000M Fiber Media Converter SC port , Internal Power Supply', '10/100/1000Base-TX to 100/1000Base-FX Media Converter is the first media converter in the market  to fulfill 100/1000M auto-sensation at fiber optic port, which increase the flexibility of the whole network.', 11, 0, 1, '', 1, '2017-10-09 02:22:13', 1507478400, NULL, '<p><span style="font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;"><strong>MAIN DESCRITION</strong></span><span style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"></span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;"></span> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">10/100/1000Base-TX to 100/1000Base-FX Media Converter is the first media converter in the market</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">to fulfill 100/1000M auto-sensation at fiber optic port, which increase the flexibility of the whole network.</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">It complies with IEEE802.3, IEEE802.3u, IEEE802.3z, IEEE802.3ab standards and supports the connection </span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">between 10Base-T, 10Base-TX, 1000Base-T, 100Base-FX and 1000Base-SX/LX.</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,2