(33, 'Fiber Switches 4*1000M + 1*10/100/1000M UTP , SC ports, singlemode ,external power supply', '', 11, 0, 2, '', 1, '2017-10-09 02:24:52', 1507478400, NULL, '<p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><strong>Main Description</strong></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">It belonged to the switch of 2000series,4 ports for 1000 Base SC, single mode and multi mode, single fiber</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and dual fibers can be selected;the max transporting distance can reach 120km, It adopts high quality network switch chip,</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and its all ports support non-blocking, across the packet forwarding; it is very suitable for data communication,video monitoring</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and relay transmission equipment during to flexible and simple usage. </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><strong>Technical parameters</strong></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(1) Operating standards:IEEE802.3/u/z/ab,10/100/1000Base-T and 1000Base-SX/LX</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(2) Flow control</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Full Duplex: IEEE802.3x flow control</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Half duplex: back pressure flow control</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(3) Connector: UTP: RJ-45:10/100/1000Mbps; fiber port: 1000Mbps</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(4).Ultra-low time-delay date transmission, completely transparent to the network protocol</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(5).Port support IEEE802.X VLAN, port monitoring.IPV6 port monitoring flux is 4K,base on MARC`s Trunking</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(6)Effectiveness of automatic link transfer</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(7).Support for spanning tree and loop detection,IGMP,MLD</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(8)Bult-in 9720Bytes long data packet</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(9) Cable: UTP: Cat.5 or 6 UTP (the max distance up to 120m)</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Multimode Fiber:50/125,62.5/125μm (the max distance up to 2KM)</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Single mode Fiber: 9/125μm (the max distance up to 120km)</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(10).Support 2 ports for SFP/FC/SC, to feel free to select optic modules for SFP/FC/SC to achieve single/multi mode or different transporting distances.</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(11).Support hot-swappable, plug and play</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Dynamic feedback the status for link connection and fault detect.</p><p><br /></p>', '<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tbody><tr class="firstRow"><td width="157"><p><strong><span style="font-size:13px;"><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;">Parameter</span></span></strong></p></td><td width="508" valign="top"><p><strong><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;"> Specifications</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td width="157"><p><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;"> Access mode</span></p></td><td width="508" valign="top"><p><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;"> 10/100/1000Mbps</span> *1   </p></td></tr><tr><td width="157"><p><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;"> Standard</span></p></td><td width="508" valign="top"><p><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;"> IEEE802.3 1000Base-T Ethernet,</span></p><p><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;"> IEEE802.3u,1000Base-TX/FX Fast Ethernet,</span></p><p><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;"> IEEE802.3x Flow control</span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="157"><p><span style="line-height:2;font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;">