(35, 'Fiber Switches with 2 * 1000M + 4*10/100/1000M UTP ,SC ports , external power supply', '', 9, 0, 2, '', 1, '2017-10-09 02:34:29', 1507478400, NULL, '<p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><strong>Main Description</strong></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">It belonged to the switch of 2000series,2 ports for 1000 Base SFP ,LC or SC,FC,ST, single mode and multi mode, single fiber</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and dual fibers can be selected;the max transporting distance can reach 120km, It adopts high quality network switch chip,</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and its all ports support non-blocking, across the packet forwarding; it is very suitable for data communication,video monitoring</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and relay transmission equipment during to flexible and simple usage. </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><strong>Technical parameters</strong></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(1) Operating standards:IEEE802.3/u/z/ab,10/100/1000Base-T and 1000Base-SX/LX</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(2) Flow control</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Full Duplex: IEEE802.3x flow control</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Half duplex: back pressure flow control</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(3) Connector: UTP: RJ-45:10/100/1000Mbps; SFP slot: 1000Mbps</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(4).Ultra-low time-delay date transmission, completely transparent to the network protocol</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(5).Port support IEEE802.X VLAN, port monitoring.IPV6 port monitoring flux is 4K,base on MARC`s Trunking</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(6)Effectiveness of automatic link transfer</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(7).Support for spanning tree and loop detection,IGMP,MLD</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(8)Bult-in 9720Bytes long data packet</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(9) Cable: UTP: Cat.5 or 6 UTP (the max distance up to 120m)</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">Multimode Fiber:50/125,62.5/125μm (the max distance up to 2KM)</p><p style="font-family