(40, 'Fiber Switches with 2*1000M FX+2*10/100/1000M UTP , SC/ST/FC/LC (SFP), external power supply', '', 0, 0, 2, '', 1, '2017-10-09 02:41:57', 1507478400, NULL, '<p><span style="font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;"><strong>MAIN DESCRIPTION</strong></span><span style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"></span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">10/100/1000Mbps adaptive fast Ethernet Optical Media Converter, with built-in 2 ports 10/100/1000Mbps</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">self-adaptive switch, converting the 4 independent 100Base-T or 1000Base-TX twisted pair electrical</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">signal with 1000Base-FX optical signal. It extends the network transmission range from 100m, the</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">l</span><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">imit of copper line, to 120Km (single mode full duplex). It supports two different types of network</span></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="line-height:1;font-family:Verdana;">connection media, 10/100/1000Base-TX and 1000Base-FX. By switching technique and storage &amp; forwarding</s