(44, 'Fiber Switches with 2*1000M SFP+4*10/100/1000M , SFP slot ,External power supply', '', 8, 0, 2, '', 1, '2017-10-09 03:03:49', 1507478400, NULL, '<p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><strong>4 ports and 2 SFP ports Gigabit ethernet optical fiber switch:</strong><strong> </strong></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">It belonged to the switch of 2000series,2 ports for 1000 Base SFP ,LC or SC, single mode and multi mode, single fiber</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and dual fibers can be selected;the max transporting distance can reach 120km, It adopts high quality network switch chip,</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and its all ports support non-blocking, across the packet forwarding; it is very suitable for data communication,video monitoring</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">and relay transmission equipment during to flexible and simple usage. </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"> </p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);"><strong>Technical parameters</strong></p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(1) Operating standards:IEEE802.3/u/z/ab,10/100/1000Base-T and 1000Base-SX/LX</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);">(2) Flow control</p><p style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-si